node.text: People often ask me “what’s Donald Trump REALLY like?” — I can say it a thousand times but, here is proof: he is, and has always been, one of the most caring, philanthropic people I know. Not to get a tax write off, but because (much like the reason he ran for President), it’s the right thing to do. There are stories out there that many have never heard, about Donald Trump buying a guy whose car broke down on the Jersey turnpike a new car, flying a sick kid across the country for life-saving medical treatment, funding a kids’ basketball team in the Bronx so that they could have another season the following year...THIS is who @realdonaldtrump is at his core. And, this video is yet another example of that and a reminder that, before he entered politics, people generally agreed that he was a great guy. #TheMoreYouKnow 💫
